That wouldn't be cool.

23:26.110 --> 23:27.945
I don't want to break their hearts.

23:28.029 --> 23:30.072
We ought to have a signal.

23:31.073 --> 23:32.449
A password.

23:33.325 --> 23:35.619
- Okay, what's the password?
- You got it.

23:35.702 --> 23:37.329
- Got what?
- The password.

23:37.579 --> 23:39.456
- The password is what?
- Exactly.

23:39.539 --> 23:41.374
- The password is "exactly"?
- No.

23:41.499 --> 23:43.668
Hold it, hold it. Slow down.

23:45.628 --> 23:48.214
- The babe walks in. You see her.
- I see her.

23:49.465 --> 23:51.550
- You come get me.
- I come get you.

23:51.884 --> 23:55.721
