so you glide by me and you say... what?

23:56.513 --> 23:57.556
Okay.

23:58.390 --> 24:00.934
- The password is "okay"?
- As far as I'm concerned.

24:01.017 --> 24:02.644
- Say the password!
- What?

24:02.936 --> 24:04.270
Say the password!

24:04.521 --> 24:06.105
The password is "what."

24:06.606 --> 24:08.900
- That's what I'm asking you.
- It's the password.

24:08.983 --> 24:11.485
- The password is "it"?
- The password is "what."

24:11.569 --> 24:12.987
"It." You just said so!

24:13.070 --> 24:15.322
- The password isn't "it," it's...
- What?

24:15.405 --> 24:16.782
- Got it.
- I got it?

24:16.865 --> 24:18.533
- Right!
- "It" or "right"?

24:19.367 --> 24:20.493
What?

24:21.578 --> 24:24.706
<i>[Dez Dickerson begins playing
80s rock song Modernaire]</i>

24:34.340 --> 24:35.883
<i>[Modernaire continues]</i>

24:48.394 --> 24:49.937
<i>[Modernaire continues]</i>

25:19.381 --> 25:20.382
Hi.

25:23.176 --> 25:27.138
I heard through the grapevine
that you had a new tune written by...

25:27.638 --> 25:29.390
...a couple of great girls.

25:29.682 --> 25:31.016
Did you hear it?

25:33.310 --> 25:35.771
I knew it. He didn't listen to it.

25:36.855 --> 25:40.317
LISA: He probably dropped it
under his bike and rolled over it.

25:43.528 --> 25:44.821
Wow. All right.

25:46.364 --> 25:47.782
You think about this.

25:47.865 --> 25:49.617
