26:23.898 --> 26:25.692
Fuck it, Wendy. Let's break.

26:25.817 --> 26:28.277
<i>PUPPET: Why should he do your music?</i>

26:28.361 --> 26:30.154
<i>He's been doing fine without it.</i>

26:30.237 --> 26:33.282
