26:50.715 --> 26:51.841
LISA: Come on.

26:51.924 --> 26:53.425
I'm so tired of this.

27:00.140 --> 27:01.266
[Door slams]

27:07.396 --> 27:08.648
You tired, too?

27:12.693 --> 27:14.737
God got Wendy's periods reversed.

27:15.070 --> 27:17.864
MATT: About every 28 days,
she starts acting nice.

27:18.115 --> 27:19.866
