27:23.578 --> 27:25.455
What difference does it make?

27:30.292 --> 27:32.211
We're still a group, right?

27:34.505 --> 27:35.923
[Door slams]

27:38.133 --> 27:41.177
MORRIS: So, what was that
you were saying about timing?

27:42.929 --> 27:44.347
[Women giggle]

27:45.014 --> 27:47.892
I like that. So cute.
Makes you look young.

27:56.984 --> 27:58.110
"What."

27:58.819 --> 28:00.320
- What?
- Right. "What."

28:00.403 --> 28:01.780
- What?
- You got it.

28:01.863 --> 28:03.156
I got it?

28:05.950 --> 28:07.618
[Rock music plays]

28:12.790 --> 28:15.375
<i>PUPPET: You don't need those girls...</i>

28:15.584 --> 28:17.085
