you didn't.

39:20.527 --> 39:21.528
Oh, yeah?

39:34.998 --> 39:38.377
[Simulated moaning with rock beat
continues playing on stereo]

39:39.669 --> 39:41.796
APOLLONIA: So who's the lucky girl?

