44:51.205 --> 44:52.957
I've got things to do.

44:56.168 --> 44:57.586
What you gonna do?

45:00.338 --> 45:01.298
Wait!

45:02.799 --> 45:04.133
Okay, straight up.

45:04.259 --> 45:07.053
I have a little group
and you'd fit in real well.

45:07.220 --> 45:09.847
Just come by. Maybe we can
work something out.

45:10.097 --> 45:11.515
Just business?

45:11.682 --> 45:14.226
You can make up your own mind.
Just come by.

45:15.185 --> 45:16.728
I know you could use the break.

45:16.812 --> 45:19.272
Don't you want to be a star? I do.

45:19.981 --> 45:22.567
This just might work out for both of us.

45:26.738 --> 45:28.489
Know any good pawnshops?

45:28.573 --> 45:29.615
Sure. Why?

45:29.740 --> 45:32.159
I'm thinking about buying a guitar.

46:01.936 --> 46:05.273
<i>[Instrumental version of Purple Rain
plays on stereo]</i>

46:18.702 --> 46:19.744
[Door slams]

46:19.828 --> 46:22.622
<i>FATHER: [Yells] You do what I say!
Do you hear me?</i>

46:24.374 --> 46:26.042
<i>You do what I say!</i>

46:26.125 --> 46:27.668
[Bang, glass shatters]

46:30.254 --> 46:32.256
<i>FATHER: You keep this place clean!</i>

46:33.424 --> 46:35.884
<i>You belong here and no place else!</i>

46:35.968 --> 46:36.969
