46:55.944 --> 46:57.154
[Mother gasps]

46:57.237 --> 46:59.698
[Suspenseful instrumental beat,
background]

47:11.208 --> 47:13.127
MOTHER: I'm just trapped here.

47:14.253 --> 47:16.296
