They call?

51:36.910 --> 51:39.204
[Blasts amplifier to distorted volume]

51:43.500 --> 51:44.500
Hey, Kid.

51:45.460 --> 51:47.503
CHICK: The boss wants to see you.

51:47.670 --> 51:49.338
